{"tid":852281,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"望住個窗口好想就咁跳落去","createTime":"2018-10-07T17:26:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T13:57:42.000Z","uid":135284,"like":70,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"51ee10344616ba690fcf81a930dc31e6ba9d4cb9","tid":852281,"uid":135284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T17:26:37.000Z","msg":"抑鬱就好似隻怪獸咁，唔知佢幾時嚟，好細微嘅嘢就可能觸發到佢出嚟<br />\n好廢好冇用，就算有朋友有男朋友都好似得自己一個，冇人明呢種感受<br />\n個心長期有舊嘢塞住係到咁，唔知隻怪獸幾時嚟<br />\n佢一嚟就抖唔到氣，床尾由好耐年前開始已經有個扣針stand by<br />\n一抖唔到氣跌返落個深淵到，就不斷落去等自己清醒返，抽離返出嚟<br />\n好驚人當自己係異類，所以將呢個自己收埋，<br />\n連我自己都唔鍾意呢個咁軟弱嘅自己，更何況其他人<br />\n呢一世你都會同呢隻怪獸共處，除非你消失，佢就會同你一齊消失"},{"pid":"5e23ced1c4bb73fe588d043b61da88b70f31ed20","tid":852281,"uid":150153,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T17:29:51.000Z","msg":"唔好咁諗唔開呀樓主 有咩事同人傾多啲啦 世界仲好美好"},{"pid":"9030a9acefdadfb0691552bbfcdde3a4f3a9f973","tid":852281,"uid":127929,"like":4,"dislike":26,"score":-22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T17:32:59.000Z","msg":"同我打返場友誼波先ok?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c71778686c3f1dc3fd96c2136fa7dc565475d01","tid":852281,"uid":127929,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T17:33:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/21/230920_c7da2202001ef3739c67954b4c9dbb31.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F21%2F230920_c7da2202001ef3739c67954b4c9dbb31.PNG&h=22f7f818&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8dc16d812ec9058b906e720b7a586ce0c00c3849","tid":852281,"uid":173419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T17:38:38.000Z","msg":"加油啊 要記住你永遠都唔係自己一個"},{"pid":"3a86ea0b226a7cf9eec6e17a5f0f0cb80e709e90","tid":852281,"uid":81195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T17:44:34.000Z","msg":"抑鬱嗰陣會諗d咩？"},{"pid":"2103f42cf69dac146634d5378551fd51df8d2